data.description: Welcome to your new cozy retreat! Nestled in a tranquil neighborhood, this charming home offers a warm and inviting atmosphere for you and your loved ones. This home is peaceful and accesible, offering the best of both worlds. It is conveniently located near schools, parks, interstate, and shopping centers. A glimpse into the delightful features that make this house a true haven are a patio and deck that may be perfect for al fresco dining or morning coffee. You can also enjoy meals in the intimate dining space it offers that seamlessly connects to the kitchen. Its perfect for intimate dinners or having friends over for a cozy get-together. Large gathering space on the lower level provides more space for hosting or relaxing. Don't miss out, call to see it!
